; Coverage for report.cc lines 1012-1019: fn_lot_date
; Tests the lot_date function which returns the date annotation from a lot
; Uses lot with date annotation to exercise the details.date branch

2024/03/15 * Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage          10 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/03/15]
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(lot_date(amount))\n" Assets:Brokerage
2024/03/15
end test
